com.adobe.fd.signatures.pki.client

Class RevocationInfoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.fd.signatures.pki.client.RevocationInfoList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RevocationInfoList
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Lists the revocation information associated with an End Entity Certificate. The Revocation Information Provided can only be of types X509CRL, OCSPRevocationInfo and OtherRevocationInfo
    Author:
    ankit
